<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得<delay8 />新年在睡覺中度過，<delay20 />
實在是太浪費時間了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新的一年<delay8 />都已經來了，<delay20 />
還是起床好好感受一下新年的氣氛<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比較舒服啦——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />新年的時候，<delay20 />你都玩些什麼啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />我應該還是會去放風箏吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然剛開始風箏總是飛不起來，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只要一搭上正確的風向，<delay20 />
就可以<delay8 />飛到很高的地方喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay20 />線斷了以後，<delay8 />
風箏總是就這樣<delay20 />
不知道飛到哪裡去就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然說到新年，<delay20 />就會想到驛站接力賽吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，<tag a="110" b="33" />的
驛站接力賽<delay20 />就要開始了──！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你問「只有我們兩個參加嗎」？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈，<delay8 />只要比對方先到下一站等著接棒，<delay20 />
就算只有兩個人也能玩接力賽喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經決定好<delay20 />今年的目標了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我早就決定好囉──！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />首先<delay8 />要練出10塊腹肌，<delay frames="30" />
接著<delay8 />鍛鍊肱三頭肌，<delay20 />
最後<delay8 />再把大腿肌練得又粗又壯！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等我把身體練得結實又強壯後，<delay20 />
就出道成為<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />選手！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay20 />這計劃太完美了──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在新年期間<delay20 />會用書法寫下今年目標嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />我已經想好<delay8 />
到底要寫什麼啦──！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />目前<delay8 />「肱二頭肌」、<delay8 />「腹肌」、<delay8 />「大腿肌」<delay20 />
這三種是我最想寫的！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「三角肌」<delay8 />也讓人難以割捨！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>